# textdomain: mcl_copper
##[ nodes.lua ]##
Copper Ore=Bakrena ruda

Some copper contained in stone, it is pretty common and can be found below sea level.=Nekaj bakra v kamnu; je precej pogost in ga je mogoče najti pod morsko gladino.

Block of Raw Copper=Blok surovega bakra
A block used for compact raw copper storage.=Blok, ki se uporablja za strnjeno shranjevanje surovega bakra.
Block of Copper=Bakren blok
A block of copper is mostly a decorative block.=Bakren blok je večinoma okrasni blok.
Waxed Block of Copper=Povoskan bakren blok
Exposed Copper=Izpostavljen baker
Exposed copper is a decorative block.=Izpostavljen baker je okrasni blok.
Waxed Exposed Copper=Povoskan izpostavljen baker
