##[ items.lua ]##
Copper Ingot=Bakrena palica
Molten Raw Copper. It is used to craft blocks.=Staljen surov baker. Uporablja se za izdelavo blokov.
Raw Copper=Surov baker
Raw Copper. Mine a Copper Ore to get it.=Surov baker. Izkopljite bakreno rudo, da ga dobite.